ing: 1 small block of Swiss cheese, cut into cubes
n: Ham and Cheese Skewers with Crunchy MailleÂ® Cornichons
des: "For a simple and tasty appetizer, simply place cornichons, cherry tomatoes, ham, and cubes of Swiss cheese on wooden skewers--and serve!"
ins:
Cut each slice of ham in 3, and roll each piece on itself to form a little square.
Slide a Maille(R) cornichon, then a cube of ham, then a cube of cheese, then a tomato on a skewer. Repeat 3 times to fill the skewer.
Repeat for each skewer.
